{"tid":1163331,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人隻貓支氣管炎？","createTime":"2019-05-20T11:35:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-21T09:18:09.000Z","uid":156380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4bddd9782ebcc343dd012ff32da80fbe1351a090","tid":1163331,"uid":156380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T11:35:25.000Z","msg":"琴日發現隻貓玩玩具會氣喘 又用口抖氣，每次抖5秒之後又冇事，諗住係咪天氣太熱，想觀察多一日。<br />\n<br />\n點知今日2點幾左右，癲左咁跑黎跑去，就開始係咁每隔5分鐘就用口抖氣，隔左30分鐘訓係到又冇事。<br />\n<br />\n 即刻book 獸醫，去左荃灣間活泉睇醫生，照左X RAY，話係支氣管炎。開左啲抗生素同氣管藥，叫我一星期後再帶黎覆診。咁我一返去就困籠同餵藥。<br />\n<br />\n有冇人隻貓都係有氣管炎？會唔會斷尾？<br />\n有冇啲咩要特別注意？有冇啲咩可以幫到佢？<br />\n隻貓嚴重上黎會點？<br />\n<br />\n我真係好擔心！"},{"pid":"9ca36f76444636443b236b55ec8a8528ff8f8d41","tid":1163331,"uid":156380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T06:47:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0edbe763eee0ddbb7857c704dee8ad7c2e90f94b","tid":1163331,"uid":58445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T07:38:44.000Z","msg":"試過 食下藥冇事"},{"pid":"dd56f81dbaa29b56ed47bec1812248334be9986b","tid":1163331,"uid":156380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0edbe763eee0ddbb7857c704dee8ad7c2e90f94b","tid":1163331,"uid":58445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T07:38:44.000Z","msg":"試過 食下藥冇事"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T09:02:50.000Z","msg":"咁都放心啲。絲打隻貓有冇話好容易就復發？<br />\n<br />\n食左兩次藥都見佢會打下噴嚏同間唔時用口抖氣就好撚驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c91938f805b4b8a511b031380a4e0cbb8b76fd3d","tid":1163331,"uid":58445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd56f81dbaa29b56ed47bec1812248334be9986b","tid":1163331,"uid":156380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0edbe763eee0ddbb7857c704dee8ad7c2e90f94b","tid":1163331,"uid":58445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T07:38:44.000Z","msg":"試過 食下藥冇事"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T09:02:50